import requests

url = "https://maps-data.p.rapidapi.com/searchmaps.php"

querystring = {"query":"schools","limit":"200","country":"us","lang":"en","lat":"17.4065","lng":"78.4772","offset":"0","zoom":"13"}

headers = {
	"X-RapidAPI-Key": "409ab7b1a3mshdad263026d55cc2p18b148jsne7679885bfe5",
	"X-RapidAPI-Host": "maps-data.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers, params=querystring)

print(response.json())

Hotels in mumbai¶

In [6]:
import requests

url = "https://maps-data.p.rapidapi.com/searchmaps.php"

querystring = {"query":"hotels","limit":"200","country":"us","lang":"en","lat":"19.0760","lng":"72.8777","offset":"0","zoom":"13"}

headers = {
	"X-RapidAPI-Key": "409ab7b1a3mshdad263026d55cc2p18b148jsne7679885bfe5",
	"X-RapidAPI-Host": "maps-data.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers, params=querystring)

print(response.json())
